<%- include partials/header.ejs%>
<%- include partials/main_nav.ejs%>


<main class="container bg-light text-dark p-5">
  <h5 class="display-4">Welcome to the <%= title %> page</h5>
<div id="carouselExampleDark" class="carousel carousel-dark slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-indicators">
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="10000">
      <img src="/Assets/images/sem_2_erd.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Entity Relational Diagram">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-light" style="opacity:0.89;">
        <h5>Project 1: Database creation </h5>
        <p >Created a database for a fictional clothing store, here you see an Entity-Relational Diagram that is from Oracle SQL Developper</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item" data-bs-interval="2000">
      <img src="/Assets/images/Client_Side_Web_Dev.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Toronto's weather on October 9 2022, 3:20 am">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-light" style="opacity:0.89;">
        <h5>Project 2: Client Side Web Development</h5>
        <p>Created JavaScript responsive web pages, for more exmaples please visit my <a href="http://studentweb.cencol.ca/ajomail/Comp125/index.html"
        class="a-link" target="blank">work</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img src="/Assets/images/CookUp-ERD.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Cook up Application ERD">
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block bg-dark text-light" style="opacity:0.89;" >
        <h5>Project 3: Database</h5>
        <p>This is another database project for Software System Design. The main purpose is for the user to input their inngredients on hand to have recipes suggested to them.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
  </button>
  <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleDark" data-bs-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
  </button>
</div>
</main>

<%- include partials/bottom_nav.ejs%>

<%- include partials/footer.ejs%>